node.text: I honestly always feel this overexposed.
Just triggering your OCD with my second button.
Hey MTV welcome to my crib!
Do not expect me to open the door like this but know I could.
Everyday at approximately 4pm @lisabattilomo states “omg look how niceeeee”.
I swear I own a neck.
If the term “whatever” had a facial expression it would be this one.
Judge if you wish, I do not care.
